<hw>authentication</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a mark on an article of trade
to indicate its origin and authenticity.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hallmark, assay-mark.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>validating the authenticity of something or
someone.</def>⟦br⟧
